              "blocks": {}
            },
            "text_64MVmA": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>In exploring my heritage through the lens of inspiring designs, and the individuals who wore them, I discovered that the history of dedication and hard work on the farm laid the foundation for my dream of becoming a fashion designer generations later.<\/p><p>Just as farm work demands perseverance and long hours, my ambition was to mirror this commitment to effort and time, through my garments. <\/p><p>By embracing sustainable practices like extensive handcraft elements and repurposing materials not only for this collection but as a <strong>genuine slow fashion designer<\/strong>, I wanted to honor and bring the hard work and life on the farm, to the catwalk. <\/p><p>[the essence of my heritage from Hessen, GER]<\/p><p><\/p>",
                "width": "fit-content",
                "max_width": "normal",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "rte",
                "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
